Author: ziyal79
Text: You're obviously not getting enough nutrients across the board. So your body is probably in ketosis, using your body fat as fuel because you're not eating enough carbs, or food more broadly, for your body to sufficiently create what you need.   That's what causes the ammonia type sweat smell anyway.
